Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_MAIN_0_SCENE_0010_01.Text:
*: You could not find her?
Oh, innocent Yayoi...
I feel for you so...

*: I hope she has fled...
We need peace, not sacrifice...
Why, Queen Pimiko...

*: My apologies...
Entrusting you with her search...
Hateful work indeed...

*: How long I wonder...
Till the queen punishes us...
Her rage knows no bounds...

*: The fear festers yet...
Orochi's appetite grows...
How long do we have...

*: Still, I remain glad...
Losing Yayoi would have hurt...
She has done no wrong...

*: Sacrificing girls...
Orochi's awful demands...
I would take no part...

*: The last sacrifice...
The swordsmith's wife; her husband...
They fled just in time...

*: Then Yayoi was next...
But she vanished soon after...
The fiend is starving...

*: Queen Pimiko too...
We know not how she will act...
I live in terror...

*: More sacrifices...
I know they will be chosen...
There's no end in sight...

*: Indeed, at your age...
The worry must be intense...
Curse that vile monster...

*: Though we must rejoice...
Now Yayoi still lives and breathes...
May it continue...

*: She must leave Jipang...
Or the queen will find her soon...
Such is her power...

*: Now, that is enough......
It's time to disperse promptly...
Act like all is well...

*: Ah, dearest Yayoi...
I pray you can stay hidden...
But I still worry...

*: I have to find her...
Before anyone else does...
This is my duty...

*: As you deserve life...
Like the bees deserve pollen...
I will protect you...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0110_010.Text: *: Look! A foreigner! Look at the funny foreigner! Hee hee!
*: So am I a foreigner to you foreigners? Hee hee! That's funny! I'm a foreigner! I'm a foreigner!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0210_010.Text: *: Waaa! Yayoi is to be sacrificed! This cannot be!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0210_020.Text: *: Hooray! Yayoi is saved! And I need no longer pretend. For you see...
*: ...I am in truth a girl! My honoured father raised me as a boy, fearing that I would be sacrificed!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0310_010.Text:
*: You ask of an orb...
I know no more of such things...
Than frogs know of flight...

*: Yet great Pimiko...
Possesses a magic sphere...
Is this what you seek...?

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0310_020.Text:
*: A deed unequalled...
In all the long years of man...
A people set free...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0410_010.Text:
*: Wise Queen Pimiko...
Ruler of heaven and earth...
Goddess and mother...

*: Obey her command...
Orochi's sacrifices...
Will keep us from harm...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0420_010.Text:
*: Welcome to Jipang...
Bless'd land of the rising sun...
Herald of morn's light...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0410_020.Text:
*: Gratitude, pure, true...
Wells within... Floods... Overwhelms...
A tumbling torrent...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0420_020.Text:
*: Welcome to Jipang...
Realm of the gossamer mists...
Home of the poets...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0410_030.Text:
*: Jipang welcomes you...
As the land welcomes the spring...
Friend, the shrine awaits!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0510_010.Text:
*: Ah, dearest Yayoi...
You must be here still hiding...
Oh, how I worry...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0510_020.Text:
*: His daughter's life saved...
Yayoi's father clings tightly...
Like the strangling vine...

*: How then to free her...?
That another might join her...
In bonds of marriage...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0610_010.Text:
*: Orochi the great...
All-devouring serpent queen...
Terror of mankind...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0610_020.Text:
*: To think the queen was...
A serpent in royal dress...
Now we may live free...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0710_010.Text: *: I travelled here to preach the word of the Goddess, our Holy Mother, but the natives worship only Queen Pimiko!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0710_020.Text: *: Queen Pimiko has passed away, and yet now the heathens bow at your feet instead! Goddess, give me strength!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0810_010.Text:
*: Welcome to Jipang...
Realm of the gossamer mists...
Home of Pimiko...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910_010.Text:
*: Sacrifice is hard...
Yet were we not to please her...
All would be destroyed...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910_020.Text:
*: Girl after young girl...
Fed in the dawn of their days...
To the sly serpent...

*: Such dark tragedy...
Even to think of it now...
Dark storm clouds gather...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910_030.Text:
*: Orochi passes...
The land lives on without her...
Truly life goes on...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910_040.Text:
*: Strange sounds echo still...
The well is their origin...
I yet wonder why...

*: There they go again...
You must have heard that, surely...
Bang, bang, thud, thud, slam...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_1210_010.Text:
*: Many moons ago...
A swordsmith and his consort...
Lived here blissfully...

*: But she was chosen...
A gift for cruel Orochi...
Thus they fled the town...

*: That is all I know...
Though in their former abode...
There is a hammer...

*: Left all on its own...
Abandoned in the forest...
A hurried escape...

*: I saw it returned...
Their home surrounded by trees...
How it misses them...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_VOLUME_1010_01.Text: {LEADER} calms the monster with a soothing voice and tells it about Monty's monster menagerie...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_VOLUME_1110_01.Text: {LEADER} calms the monster with a soothing voice and tells it about Monty's monster menagerie...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_1510_010.Text:
*: Distant southern isle...
Rumour meets reality...
Treasure lost to time...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_House1_SUB_0_ACTOR_0110_.Text:
*: My daughter, chosen...
She is to be sacrificed...
Clouds engulf my heart...

*: A life without fear...
Spring days with my one daughter...
And all thanks to you...

*: While lone drinkers sigh...
He who drinks with his daughter...
Beams like a new sun!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_House1_SUB_0_ACTOR_0220_.Text: *: Holy Mother! Sainted Goddess! Deliver the daughter of this wayward heathen from evil, that he might know Your glory!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_House1_SUB_0_ACTOR_0310_.Text:
The days of sunshine...
The evenings of soft moonlight...
All are thanks to you...

Stay awhile, wand'rer...
Bask in that which you gave us...
Revel in sweet peace...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_House2_SUB_0_ACTOR_0110_.Text:
*: A boy child! Praise be!
Though girls are fair as flowers...
The serpent plucks them...

*: No more must she hide...
The truth spreads its wings and flies...
Son becomes daughter...

*: Raised as if a boy...
My daughter becomes like one...
Ground grows as planted...

*: But nurtured with care...
Healthy roots in good soil grow...
No matter the seed...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_House2_SUB_0_ACTOR_0310_.Text: *: Did I tell you that I am really a girl? After pretending for so long, it feels strange to say it...
*: But I am happy! For now I can grow to be like my heroine Yayoi!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_House3_SUB_0_ACTOR_0110_.Text:
*: Will I be the next...?
Will I be the serpent's prey...?
Can no one save me...?

*: No longer the fear...
Of being chosen to die...
Bless you, my saviour...

*: My brother escaped...
Orochi came for his bride...
Luckily, she lives...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Storehouse_SUB_0_ACTOR_0.Text:
What you have not seen...
Cannot do you any harm...
Unsee me, I beg!

A farewell to home...
Last glimpse of hearth and mother...
Give me this at least...

You are not local...
Traveller, please spare my life...
Tell no one of me...

Oh, thank you so much...
I swear I will not forget...
Your sweet compassion...

I am indeed her...
I was to be sacrificed...
My name is Yayoi...

I prepared myself...
I waited to be taken...
But then I noticed...

My bindings were loose...
Freedom had knocked on my door...
That was how I fled...

The fiend Orochi...?
Yes, I can share what I know...
If it will help you...

It was years ago...
The beast was found in a cave...
To the east of here...

Orochi spoke thus...
<6>Offer up your maidens' lives...
Or I will end you...<9>

No one could resist...
Therefore we do as she says...
Years and years of loss...

Our ruler searches...
She needs to sacrifice me...
To protect Jipang...

If she learns of you...
That you found me; she will rage...
Flee while you still can...

And the monster's lair...
That cursed cave to the east...
You must avoid it...

Thank you, traveller...
For not handing me over...
To that ghastly fiend...

You must leave at once...
And avoid the eastern cave...
Please promise me this...

At last, I am free...
Death's shadow no longer looms...
Long live our hero...

*: We live now in peace...
Our days long, our songs joyful...
Thanks to you, saviour...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_VOLUME_0010_.Text:
*: Noble Majesty!
Blood flows like a red river!
Let me tend your wound!

*: But whence does it flow?
How came you to be hurt so?
Who dares harm our queen?

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0110_0.Text: Who are you? Have you business with me?
I see now what you are... Visitors from a foreign land.
Know that outlanders are not welcome within Jipang's borders.
And that will not change any time soon.
Begone! I will not trade words with barbarians!
I do not plan on changing my nation's ways for your sake.
Begone! I will not trade words with barbarians!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_VOLUME_0110_.Text: Queen Pimiko projects her voice directly into {LEADER}'s mind!
You and you alone have seen my true form.
Your silence will buy your life. Do you accept my terms?
Mmhmhmhm! A wise decision indeed... You are not quite so foolish as you appear.
This is what you have decided? Very well.

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0140_0.Text: Then I shall devour you, and leave not a solitary scrap of flesh on your bones!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0150_0.Text: I...am the rightful ruler of this land! You... You are nothing but an insignificant insect...
Thus far, I have crushed any and all resistance that stood in my way... How could I fall now?

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_BATTLE_END_0.Text: And so it was discovered that Pimiko was in fact Orochi all along.
Orochi abused her position of power, forcing the village to offer up its maidens for her to devour.
The shocking truth spread through the village like wildfire.
After the battle, {HERO} spent the night at the shrine to rest and recuperate. Then, the next day...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_ACTOR_0170_0.Text: You've had quite the ordeal, haven't you...
Well done, brave adventurer. You have taken yet another step on your journey to restore peace to the realm.
You must gather the orbs and take them to the shrine of the Everbird.
Know that I will be ever praying for your safety...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0210_01.Text:
*: Herein dwells our queen...
Pimiko, saviour, mistress...
Bright as the noon sun...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0210_02.Text:
*: Here dwells Pimiko...
Or so I might have spoken...
Had Her sun not set...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0210_03.Text:
*: Pimiko's dwelling...
Free now for the use of all...
Doors closed, now open...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0310_01.Text:
*: Clumsy foreigners...
Their garb, strange and ungainly...
Ugly ducklings, all...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0320_01.Text:
*: The queen's sun has set...
It will not rise till morning...
Come again with dawn...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0310_02.Text:
*: A mighty hero...
A bright sun amid dull stars...
Bathes us with its light...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0310_03.Text:
*: A god's word is law...
But to hold on too tightly...
Is to lose one's grasp...

*: Orochi saw this...
Thus was our god made godless...
And our faith betrayed...

*: Now, free of our god...
We must grow this land anew...
And learn to tend it...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0410_01.Text:
*: Our queen's powers grow...
Her gifts, ever more wondrous...
Her magic, divine...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0410_02.Text:
*: Give thanks, one and all...
From the depths of your being...
Salvation is ours!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0510_01.Text:
*: Mighty Pimiko...
Bowing before the serpent...
Must secretly seethe...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0510_03.Text:
*: Ideas not our own...
Seeds blown from distant gardens...
May nurture our land...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0610_01.Text:
*: Pimiko's quarters...
Dwelling place of the God Queen...
Seat of the sun...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0610_02.Text:
*: Wicked Orochi...
Guileful cuckoo in our midst...
Deadly deceiver...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0610_03.Text:
*: Democracy calls...
But its cry echoes, hollow...
Through arid canyons...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0720_01.Text:
*: The queen is injured...
Life ebbs like the ocean tide...
Leave this place, stranger!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0810_01.Text: *: I travelled here to preach the word of the Goddess, our Holy Mother.

*: But instead, I sermonise on methods of government, and means of production.
The Goddess moves in mysterious ways indeed...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910_01.Text:
*: Sacrificed maidens...
Chosen by wise Pimiko...
Marked out for greatness...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910_02.Text:
*: The dread serpent's fangs...
Gnashing, find their target's heart...
A queen falls, unseen...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910_03.Text:
*: Moon rises, none sleep...
All dwell on Jipang's future...
All ponder its past...

*: And what fuels their thought...?
The fruits of the fertile earth...
Bread leavened with love...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_1010_01.Text:
*: Were the serpent slain...
The queen would surely be glad...
As would her people...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_1010_02.Text:
*: Deceiving serpent...
Secretly usurps a queen...
Night falls on the land...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_SUB_0_ACTOR_1010_03.Text:
*: So it is abroad...
And so too could it be here...
Fields, ploughed, yearn for seed...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Room_MAIN_0_ACTOR_1110_0.Text:
*: For all in Jipang...
I raise up my voice in thanks...
To you, brave <IfSolo(hero,heroes)>...

My most humble thanks...
I have been spared thanks to you...
A new lease of life...

I fear more monsters...
Tricking us, in human form...
How could we stop them?

*: That such a foul beast...
Could live among us unseen...
Saddens me greatly...

*: My daughter, Yayoi...
Saved from a fate most gruesome...
Tears for the others...

That ghastly serpent...
Doubtless felled Queen Pimiko...
A true tragedy...

*: It falls to we few...
To bury those who perished...
Memories live on...

*: A small gift for you...
Mere trifle though it may be...
Pray accept our thanks...

Take care on your way...
The path long and dangerous...
My thoughts are with you...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_Storehouse_SearchObj_Pot.Text:
Eek! There's a head inside!
Wait! It's a whole person!

Txt_Talk_Jipang_BattleRoad_SUB_0_ACTOR_0.Text:
*: How unexpected...
That a well of all places...
Such strangeness would hold...

*: Oh, where am I now...?
Am I dead...? Is this limbo...?
Or could it be hell...

*: A sight to behold...
Monsters fight and do battle...
I can hardly wait...

*: This place is so strange...
I cannot comprehend it...
Yet pleasure I gain!

*: Did you see that beast?
The creature in that last match...
Strong beyond compare...

*: Monsters with such might...
Summoned from all four corners...
What fights await us...

Hello there, hero...
I am compelled to thank you...
For all you have done...

Saviour of Jipang...
Our fair land is in your debt...
Now and evermore...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_BattleRoad_Arena_SUB_0_S.Text:
*: Welcome all fight fans...
To the monster arena...
Rank-10 tournament...

*: Welcome all fight fans...
To the monster arena...
It's rank 11...

*: Match 1 will now start...
Competitors step forward...
And prepare to fight...

*: The thrill of battle...
Butterflies in the stomach...
Get ready to brawl...

Txt_Talk_Jipang_BattleRoad_Arena_SUB_0_B.Text:

Taste of victory still fresh...
It's our challenger...

*: Now on to match {VALUE}...
Competitors step forward...
And prepare to fight...

*: The final match-up...
Monsters poised to do battle...
Winner takes it all...

*: Two teams will battle...
The fight of the century...
Despair or glory...

*: No turning back now...
Competitors step forward...
It's your time to shine...

*: Victory awaits...
Rank 10, the final match-up...
Ultimate showdown...

*: The thrill of battle...
Butterflies in the stomach...
Get ready to brawl...

*: How could this happen?
The challenger defeated...
Terrible outcome...

*: Unable to win...
Match {VALUE}, eliminated...
Knocked out from rank 10...

*: The tourney concludes...
Rank 10 has now been conquered...
A perfect triumph...

*: With rank 10 beaten...
A new challenge beckons you...
Rank 11 calls...

*: Thanks to all fighters...
Incredible exertions...
A round of applause...

*: The path continues...
New challenges yet to come...
Thank you for fighting...
You and your monsters share a bond unbreakable...
Your skill is unmatched. However, do not think us defeated...
You have proven yourself worthy of the title of <6>victor<9>...
Nothing shall stand in your way now...
It appears you underestimated us...
Return when you have unlocked your full potential...

*: Winner of match {VALUE}...
Taste of victory still fresh...
It's our challenger...

*: Now on to match {VALUE}...
Competitors step forward...
And prepare to fight...

*: The final match-up...
Monsters poised to do battle...
Winner takes it all...

*: Two teams will battle...
The fight of the century...
Despair or glory...

*: No turning back now...
Competitors step forward...
It's your time to shine...

*: Victory awaits...
Rank 11, the last match...
Ultimate showdown...

*: The thrill of battle...
Butterflies in the stomach...
Get ready to brawl...

*: How could this happen...
The challenger defeated...
Terrible outcome...

*: Unable to win...
Match {VALUE}, eliminated...
From rank 11...

*: The tourney concludes...
Winner of rank 11...
A perfect triumph...

*: Nothing more to prove...
Legend of the arena...
Congratulations...

*: Thanks to all fighters...
Incredible exertions...
A round of applause...

*: The path continues...
New challenges yet to come...
Thank you for fighting...
When I first saw you, fresh-faced and green as you like, I never thought you'd make it this far... Time for me to pull out all the stops!
I<--->I can't believe I lost! I have to say, I was pretty sure I'd wipe the floor with you...
Don't get too disheartened, though. If you ever need anything from my Party Planning Place, or want a rematch here, just let me know!
